					"value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> The oath angel sees a creature that has breaken its oath willingly (or a creature under the effects of Oathbound breaks the oath willingly).</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong>The oath angel punishes the oath breaker, imposing on him a -1 Status to all its saves against fear and a -1 Status to all its attack rolls. The oath angel can target with this effect a creature that was under the effect of the angel's Oathbound as long as they're on the same planet. A creature can end this condition by demonstrating its repentance by conducting an @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.7Fd4lxozd11MQ55N] Ritual or with an heroic deed or sacrifice.</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.monster-homebrewery.effects.pED6xq6IdMEhY1Fn]{Effect: Oathbreaker}</p>",
